217
00:09:57,185 --> 00:09:58,561
Com razão.

218
00:10:02,190 --> 00:10:03,191
Querido?

219
00:10:03,441 --> 00:10:04,233
Sona.

220
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:09,780
Você está encrencado.

221
00:10:14,076 --> 00:10:16,037
